getty service
getty@tty1.service
What getty does:
Displays:
login:
Waits for username & password
After login, starts a shell (bash)
ğŸ‘‰ You get:
user@server:~$
âœ” Used in servers
âœ” Lightweight
âœ” No GUI
Case 2: Desktop â†’ GUI Login
What systemd starts:
Display Manager service
